sources.style\\main.sass:
@import "viewports.scss"
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;700&display=swap');
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300&display=swap');

/* Variables *\
$primary-font: 'Poppins', sans-serif
$secondary-font: 'Montserrat', sans-serif

$dark-colour: #131313
$accent-colour: #F1EDED

/* General *\
html
  height: 100vh
  scroll-behavior: smooth

body
  margin: 0
  height: 100vh
  background-color: $dark-colour
  font-family: $primary-font

*, *:before, *:before
  box-sizing: border-box

/* Navigation Bar *\
.container-navigation
  position: fixed
  width: 100%
  padding: 1em
  height: 100px
  z-index: 999

.hamburger
  position: relative
  left: 95%

.container-menu
  position: relative
  display: none
  top: 15%
  width: 100%
  
ul
  position: absolute 
  list-style-type: none
  margin: 0
  padding: 0
  left: 75% 
  width: 100%
 
  li
    display: inline
    a
      color: $accent-colour
      font-family: $secondary-font
      font-size: 20px
      padding-right: 75px

    a:hover
      color: white

/* Header / Hero Section *\  
.container-header
  height: 1080px

  .header-hero-titles
    position: relative
    left: 50%
    transform: translateX(-50%)
    width: 548px
    height: 124px
    top: 200px
    opacity: 100

    #hero-section-title
      position: relative
      margin: 0

      font-style: normal
      font-weight: bold
      font-size: 64px
      line-height: 85px
      text-align: center

      color: $accent-colour

    #hero-section-figcaption
      position: relative
      margin: 0

      font-family: $secondary-font
      font-style: normal
      font-weight: 300
      font-size: 32px
      line-height: 39px
      text-align: center
      letter-spacing: -0.05em

      color: $accent-colour

  #mountains-01
    position: absolute
    width: 100%
    height: 365px
    left: 0px
    top: 615px
    z-index: 1

  #mountains-02
    position: absolute
    width: 100%
    height: 430px
    left: 0px
    top: 521px
    z-index: 0

  #fixed-hero-image
    position: absolute
    z-index: -100
    width: 100%
    left: 0
    top: -10%

  #icon-scroll,
  #icon-scroll:before
    position: absolute
    left: 50%

  #icon-scroll
    width: 31px
    height: 62px
    margin-left: -20px
    top: 25%
    margin-top: -35px
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px $accent-colour
    border-radius: 15.5px
    z-index: 2
   
  #icon-scroll:before
    content: ''
    width: 13px
    height: 13px
    background: $accent-colour
    margin-left: -6px
    top: 8px
    border-radius: 15.5px
    animation-duration: 1.8s
    animation-iteration-count: infinite
    animation-name: scroll
    z-index: 2
   
  @keyframes scroll
    0%
      opacity: 1

    100%
      opacity: 0
      transform: translateY(43px)

/* Work Section *\
  
.container-work
  height: 1000px

  #work-title
    left: 50%
    transform: translateX(-50%)
    text-align: center
    font-weight: bold
    color: $accent-colour

    opacity: 0
    transition: opacity 4s
  
  .opacity-scroll
    opacity: 1 !important
  
  #work-figcaption
    left: 50%
    transform: translateX(-50%)
    text-align: center
    color: $accent-colour

    font-family: $secondary-font
    font-size: 32px
    line-height: 39px
    letter-spacing: -0.05em
    text-align: center

    opacity: 0
    transition: opacity 4s

  .opacity-scroll-2
    opacity: 1 !important

  .carousel
    height: 100%

  .carousel a
    top: 50px
    height: 800px
    width: 800px

/* About Section *\
/* Contact Section *\
.container-contact
  position: relative
  height: 847px
  margin-top: 150px

  .decorative-title
    position: absolute
    left: 46.5%
    opacity: 0.02
    color: white
    
    .deco-title-01
      font-size: 288px
      font-weight: bold

    .deco-title-02
      font-size: 220px
      font-weight: bold

  .contact-title
    position: absolute
    left: 50%
    transform: translateX(-50%)
    top: 160px
    text-align: center

    .title-co
      font-family: $primary-font
      font-weight: bold
      color: $accent-colour
      line-height: 85px
      letter-spacing: -0.05em

    .subtitle-co
      font-family: $secondary-font
      color: $accent-colour
      font-size: 32px
      line-height: 39px
      letter-spacing: -0.05em

      width: 686px

  .contact-button
    width: 269px
    height: 60px
    border-radius: 25px
    margin-top: 93px

    border: none

    font-family: $primary-font
    font-size: 24px
    font-weight: bold

    transition: width 0.5s, font-size 0.5s

  .contact-button:hover
    width: 279px
    font-size: 26px

    cursor: pointer

.container-socials-link
  position: relative
  top: 72px

  #socials-linkedin
    position: relative
    margin-right: 69px

.side-decoration-group
  position: absolute
  width: 437px
  height: 383px
  left: 70px
  top: 295px

  #deco-bottom
    position: relative
    left: 18.81%
    right: 18.81%
    top: 85.56%
    bottom: 1.91%

  #deco-bubble-bottom
    position: absolute
    left: 36.74%
    right: 43.97%
    top: 67.52%
    bottom: 8.66%
  
  #deco-bubble-right
    position: absolute
    left: 54.19%
    right: 11.27%
    top: 0%
    bottom: 57.33%

  #deco-bubble-left
    position: absolute
    left: 16.7%
    right: 58.58%
    top: 24.02%
    bottom: 45.17%

  #deco-dot-1
    position: absolute
    left: 64.78%
    right: 32.16%
    top: 64.13%
    bottom: 32.38%
  
  #deco-dot-2
    position: absolute
    left: 69.95%
    right: 26.99%
    top: 58.5%
    bottom: 38.01%

  #deco-dot-3
    position: absolute
    left: 65.96%
    right: 30.99%
    top: 54.88%
    bottom: 41.63%

  #deco-dot-4
    position: absolute
    left: 69.25%
    right: 27.69%
    top: 50.6%
    bottom: 45.92%

  #deco-dot-5
    position: absolute
    left: 64.43%
    right: 32.51%
    top: 44.16%
    bottom: 52.35%

/* Footer Section *\

.footer-container
  position: relative
  height: 250px

  background-color: #181818
  opacity: 0.5

  .footer-name
    position: relative
    margin: 0
    left: 41px
    top: 30px

    font-family: Poppins
    font-style: normal
    font-weight: bold
    font-size: 24px
    line-height: 36px
    letter-spacing: -0.05em

    color: $accent-colour

  .footer-figcaption
    position: relative
    left: 41px
    top: 30px

    font-family: $secondary-font
    font-style: normal
    font-weight: 300
    font-size: 14px
    line-height: 17px
    letter-spacing: -0.065em

    color: $accent-colour

  .linkedin-mini
    position: absolute
    left: 41px
    top: 94px
    margin-right: 21px
    width: 30px

  .dribbble-mini
    position: absolute
    left: 82px
    top: 94px
    width: 30px

  .image-credits
    position: absolute
    left: 41px
    top: 161px
    width: 100px

    font-size: 10px
    color: $accent-colour

    a
      text-decoration: none
      color: $accent-colour
      font-weight: bold

  .unsplash-img
    position: absolute
    left: 41px
    top: 197px
